  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba3 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1  \u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Railway Station Officers' Association Important Notice on Railway Fare Increase",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Railway Station Officers Association has mentioned that due to legal issues, the railway fare increase which was to be implemented from midnight the next day has been postponed till further notification is issued.",
        "The cabinet gave its approval to revise the train fare as mentioned by the former transport minister Bandula Gunawardena that the train fare should be increased to compensate for the increase in bus fare.",
        "Accordingly, it was mentioned that it has been decided to fix the initial fare of 10 rupees in the train service to 20 rupees and the initial fare for the second class to 50 rupees. However, due to the emergence of legal issues related to the increase in fares, it has been decided to suspend the fare increase until the re-announcement of the railway station principal association.",
        "It is noteworthy that the railway fare was last revised in the year 2018. The Railway Department has urged the government to increase the railway fare due to fuel shortage and fuel price hike."
      ],
